text:
1 of the better Hainanese Chicken Rice around. The chicken meat is very soft and tender. The sauce that comes with the meat is really tasty and goes very well with the rice.

Only $3.80 for Chicken Breast meat with rice and $5 for Chicken Thigh with rice. Honestly, it’s not only nice, it’s also cheap.

Pretty alright roast chicken noodle($4) (soup come with it is pretty good too!),

Curry chicken noodle($5.50) has nice soup.

Pretty healthy ish too comes with greens, feel like not many of these food usually comes with greens.
Chicken meat literally melts in the mouth and the skin was so smooth. The fragrance of the chicken sauce added points to the whole meal. It’s only $5 which is really affordable.
Hidden gem. Stall is quite new and tried their curry chicken mee. Broth is delicious match with fresh tender chicken. Will try their chicken rice next time.

New kid on the block so went to try it out

Ordered a plate with extra meat

I think I got ripped off ?
$8

Additional rice is $1
